  "text": "The measures of the two subdimensions of individualized consideration come from [CITATION_1] transformational leadership scale, which draws on [CITATION_2] research for supportive leadership (reported Cronbach's alpha: 0.92, sample item: My superior considers my personal feelings when implementing actions that will affect me) and House (1998) study for developmental leadership (reported Cronbach's alpha: 0.88), (sample item: My superior encourages staff to improve their job-related skills).",
